        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<table><thead><tr><th>扩展名</th><th align="left">描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/adguard-%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/pdffkfellgipmhklpdmokmckkkfcopbh">AdGuard 广告拦截器</a></td><td align="left">一款无与伦比的广告拦截扩展，用以对抗各式广告与弹窗</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/tampermonkey/iikmkjmpaadaobahmlepeloendndfphd">Tampermonkey</a></td><td align="left">世界上最流行的用户脚本管理器</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/global-speed-%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/mjhlabbcmjflkpjknnicihkfnmbdfced">Global Speed Plus</a></td><td align="left">设置视频和音频的默认速度</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/convertio/ncpjiachjgcccbfiganbhheoaappecgn">Convertio</a></td><td align="left">在线将文件从一种格式转换为另一种格式</td></tr><tr><td><a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/itab%E6%96%B0%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E9%A1%B5/inedkoakiaeepjoblbiiipedngonadhn?hl=zh-CN">iTab新标签页</a></td><td align="left">iTab是一个好看好用的自定义卡片式浏览器新标签页扩展</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="一、AdGuard-广告拦截器"><a href="#一、AdGuard-广告拦截器" class="headerlink" title="一、AdGuard 广告拦截器"></a>一、AdGuard 广告拦截器</h1><p>1.打开AdGuard广告拦截器扩展安装界面（<a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/adguard-%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A8/pdffkfellgipmhklpdmokmckkkfcopbh">传送门</a>）</p><p>2.点击获取进行安装</p><p><img src="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08/Edge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A81.png"></p><p>3.在弹出的配置 AdGuard 扩展页面中打开前四个设置</p><p><img src="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08/Edge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/AdGuard%E5%B9%BF%E5%91%8A%E6%8B%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%99%A82.png"></p><h1 id="二、Tampermonkey（油猴脚本）"><a href="#二、Tampermonkey（油猴脚本）" class="headerlink" title="二、Tampermonkey（油猴脚本）"></a>二、Tampermonkey（油猴脚本）</h1><h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>1.打开tampermonkey扩展安装界面（<a href="https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/tampermonkey/iikmkjmpaadaobahmlepeloendndfphd">传送门</a>）</p><p>2.点击获取进行安装</p><p><img src="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08/Edge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/tampermonkey%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A81.png"></p><h2 id="获取脚本"><a href="#获取脚本" class="headerlink" title="获取脚本"></a>获取脚本</h2><p>1.打开Greasy Fork脚本网站（<a href="https://greasyfork.org/zh-CN">传送门</a>）</p><p><img src="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08//Edge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/tampermonkey%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A82.png"></p><p>2.搜索需要的脚本</p><p>3.安装脚本</p><p><img src="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08/Edge%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95/tampermonkey%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A83.png"></p><p>4.打开需要使用脚本的网站</p><p>5.脚本即可生效使用</p><a class="btn-beautify blue larger" href="https://fastly.jsdelivr.net/gh/chenzwqs/chenzwqs.github.io/2022/06/08/Edge浏览器扩展/视频.mp4" title="查看视频教程"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>查看视频教程</span></a> 视频较卡顿，建议下载后观看]]></content>
      
      
